OL,3,CGeneral election 2024: The view from
OL,4,CDowning Street... in Ashfield
OL,6,FLittle did he know that his
OL,7,Fconstituents would be going to the
OL,8,Fpolls so soon in the General Election.
OL,10,FBefore he won the seat in 2019,
OL,11,FAshfield had been a Red Wall
OL,12,Fstronghold, voting Labour from 1979,
OL,13,Ffor a 40-year streak.
OL,15,FNow, Labour wants it back, but Reform
OL,16,FUK will be desperate to maintain their
OL,17,Ffirst seat in the House of Commons.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
