OL,3,CGeneral election 2024: The view from
OL,4,CDowning Street... in Ashfield
OL,6,FWith that in mind, I went to Downing
OL,7,FStreet. Not the one in London, but the
OL,8,Fone in Sutton-in-Ashfield, to talk to
OL,9,Fvoters.
OL,11,FFirst, I met Dan, while he got his
OL,12,Fsignature short back-and-sides.
OL,14,FHe told me he's already decided which
OL,15,Fside he'll pick on July 4. He said:
OL,16,F"Keir Starmer - I think we should vote
OL,17,Ffor Labour again round here."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
