OL,3,CGeneral election 2024: The view from
OL,4,CDowning Street... in Ashfield
OL,6,FDown the road, Rezgar Naby runs Sutton
OL,7,FTyres and Auto Centre. Most Parties
OL,8,Fare launching their manifestos this
OL,9,Fweek - but Rezgar worries they'll put
OL,10,Fthe brakes on as soon as the campaign
OL,11,Fis over.
OL,13,F"Before they come in power they
OL,14,Fadvertise, they manifest, they say
OL,15,F'we're going to create jobs, we're
OL,16,Fgoing to do this for the NHS', but
OL,17,Fonce they come in power they grab the
OL,18,Fpower and that's it."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
