OL,3,CGeneral election 2024: The view from
OL,4,CDowning Street... in Ashfield
OL,6,FThroughout the day, we spoke to a
OL,7,Fnumber of people to try and get some
OL,8,Fsense of who they might vote for.
OL,10,FLee Anderson's name came up more than
OL,11,Fonce - and the odd person mentioned
OL,12,FLabour or the Tories.
OL,14,FOf course, that's just the handful of
OL,15,Fpeople we came across - it's in no way
OL,16,Frepresentative of the whole
OL,17,Fconstituency.
OL,19,FBut the sentiment we came across more
OL,20,Fthan any other? Skepticism that any
OL,21,Fpoliticians would change things.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
