OL,3,CGeneral election 2024: The view from
OL,4,CDowning Street... in Ashfield
OL,6,FRebecca Moore lives at Number 10
OL,7,FDowning Street - but that's as close
OL,8,Fas she comes to politics.
OL,10,F"I'm not very political," she told me.
OL,11,F"Older people are more into it, but if
OL,12,Fyou talk to my mates of my age they're
OL,13,Fnot really bothered - they just don't
OL,14,Fwant to get into it."
OL,16,FMy final stop is Mr John's Salon,
OL,17,Fwhere John Rushton has been cutting
OL,18,Fand styling hair for 50 years - a far
OL,19,Flonger lifespan than most politicians.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
