OL,3,CGeneral election 2024: The view from
OL,4,CDowning Street... in Ashfield
OL,6,FHe tells me the three biggest issues
OL,7,Fin Ashfield are "the cost of living,
OL,8,Fthe NHS and the state of the roads."
OL,10,FWhile many people I met were
OL,11,Fpessimistic about Ashfield's future -
OL,12,Fand how much politicians really care
OL,13,Fabout the constituency - John was full
OL,14,Fof optimism.
OL,16,FHe feels lucky to live in the UK and
OL,17,FAshfield in particular, and tells me
OL,18,F"we don't realise how lucky we are."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
